<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5286531>
    dc:description "FIGURES 90–98. Sprattia spearei sp. nov. 90, Cephalic end, apical view. 91, Cephalic end, lateral view. 92, Anterior end female, lateral view. 93, Caudal end, male, showing fine cloacal alae, one pair of pedunculate papillae and papillae clustered around cloacal opening, ventrolateral view. 94, Caudal end female, lateral view. 95, Caudal end male, lateral view. 96, Left spicule, lateral view. 97, Right spicule, lateral view. 98, Vulva and vagina uterina, female, lateral view. Scale bars: Figs 90, 91 = 20 µm. Figs 92–98 = 50 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5286531/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

